ocemr for Debian
----------------

New Install -

    1). Setup a Database: 

	- SQLite -

	-- settings.py --
	DATABASE_ENGINE = 'sqlite3'
	DATABASE_NAME = '/var/lib/ocemr/db/ocemr.db'
	-----------------

	$ sudo -u www-data /usr/share/ocemr/util/initialize_sqlite_db.sh


	- MySQL -


	- PostgreSQL -

    2). Enable the website:

	$ sudo a2dissite default
	$ sudo a2ensite ocemr
	$ sudo /etc/init.d/apache2 reload


